name: Battle Talent Demo
summary:
⚔️Full Version is released!!⚔️
https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/8752849024786000/

Battle Talent is a challenging physics-based roguelite sword-fighting game.

Tired of fighting boring enemies? Battle Talent has created for you a mega seamless procedural dungeon. The full version with over 80 enemy variants, 100 weapons, 60 perks, and multiple landscapes that change each time.

Battle Talent brings physics driven creatures to life. You'll get to epic boss battles like you've never experienced...
